Contains:   The first major arc ("act") of "Mind the Gap",
            spanning issues one thru fifteen.


   Mind the Gap 01-05 - Act One - Intimate Strangers (2012) (Dgtl-TPB-HR) (MM-PhD)
   Mind the Gap 06-10 - Act One - Wish You Were Here (2012) (Dgtl-TPB-HR) (MM-PhD)
   Mind the Gap 11-12 - Act One - Out of Bodies      (2013) (Dgtl-TPB-HR) (MM-PhD)
   Mind the Gap 13-15 - Act One - RIPeterssen        (2013) (Dgtl-TPB-HR) (MM-PhD)


    ( compiled from the highest-quality releases, which turned out to be the single-
      issue set "Mind the Gap 001-015 (2012-2013) (Digital-HR) (Minutemen-PhD)",
      plus "Mind the Gap Vol 1-3 (2012-2014) (Digital TPB) (Empire)" for the extras )

    ( each volume bookended with an exhaustive cover gallery, as well as the
      dramatis personae pages not included in the original trade editions )
